  "transcript": [
    "> change the requirements so that the two best departure times (where one of them is always the fastest route) are returned to the frontend.",
    "\n\nLet me first look at the current requirements and understand the existing setup.\n[Tool uses: fs_read]",
    "Now let me look at the current Lambda handler and frontend to understand the existing implementation:\n[Tool uses: fs_read]",
    "Now I have a clear picture. The current setup fetches 1 trip per route (`calc_number_of_trips=1`) and returns all routes sorted by arrival. The change needed is:\n\n1. Return exactly the **two best departure times** (not all routes)\n2. One of them must always be the **fastest** (earliest arrival)\n\nLet me update the requirements and solution design:\n[Tool uses: fs_write]",
    "> n",
